<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.1">
<l>kātil kaṭippiṭ ṭu<supplied>k</supplied>kaliṅ  kamuṭuttu</l>
<l>tātu nallataṇ ṇantuḻāy koṭaṇintu</l>
<l>pōtu maṟuttup puṟamē vantuniṉṟīr</l>
<l>ētuk kituveṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ignoring the time, you came and stood outside,</l>
<l>Wearing an earring in your ear, having put on [fine] clothes,</l>
<l>And adorning [yourself] with fine, fresh tulasī with pollen;</l>
<l>What is it for? What is this? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
